---
import NahiyanKhanLogo from "@/assets/nahiyan_khan.svg?raw";
---

<div
	x-data
	class="flex h-screen w-full flex-col justify-center border-x border-b border-borderDivider"
>
	<div class="mb-8 w-11/12 text-textProminent">
		<div
			x-ref={"nahiyankhan"}
			x-init="$store.state.nahiyankhanHeight = $refs.nahiyankhan.getBoundingClientRect().height"
			@scroll.window="$store.state.nahiyankhan = $refs.nahiyankhan.getBoundingClientRect().top"
			x-on:resize.window="$store.state.nahiyankhanHeight = $refs.nahiyankhan.getBoundingClientRect().height"
		>
			<Fragment set:html={NahiyanKhanLogo} />
		</div>
	</div>
	<p class="subtitle-large mb-20 w-11/12 text-[2.1rem] leading-[1.75]">
		Am an engineer. Am a designer. Am both? Am neither? Definitions are arbitrary. Existential
		crisis is real. But 9 to 5, I lead design systems strategy and infrastructure to implement craft
		at scale.
	</p>
</div>
